# This directory's .so files are NOT committed — they're built fresh
# inside the enterprise Docker build by the cross-compile RUN clause
# that prepare-dockerfile.sh injects (same pattern as the time-freezing
# pkg/util/time/assets/ dir).
#
# The repo-root .gitignore ignores *.so and *.c globally; the negations
# below re-allow only the source, build script, and this file itself.

!cbshim.c
!build.sh
!README.md
!.gitignore
